data.revised_prompt: Create an illustration reminiscent of a 1970s or 1980s sword and sorcery novel. Aim for a hand-drawn aesthetic, common in pulp-style books. Depict a scene where a strong, adventurous character of undefined gender wields a majestic sword, standing before an imposing, shadowy castle. The character should have a darker complexion and be dressed in classic fantasy attire, glistening under the moonlight. Swirls of mystical energy should flow from the sword, further conjuring a surreal and enchanting atmosphere found in fantastical pulps.
